{{der|zh|sit}}. Cognate with {{cog|cdm|दोङःसा|tr=doŋʔ‑|t=to end; to cease}}, {{cog|cnh||tr=doŋ / doʔŋ|t=to end}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

{{zh-ref|Wang (1982)}} derives {{och-l|冬|winter}} from this word.

